1RPC.io strengthens Base’s ecosystem by providing a secure, private, and user-friendly gateway to blockchain interactions:Creators and NFT Platforms: Base’s NFT platforms, like Zora, benefit from 1RPC’s privacy protections, ensuring artists’ transactions remain secure and untracked.
DeFi Protocols: DeFi users on Base rely on 1RPC’s phishing protections to safely interact with protocols, reducing risks in high-value transactions.
Developers: 1RPC’s tools empower Base developers to build scalable, privacy-focused dApps, aligning with Base’s mission to onboard millions to Web3.
Retail Users: The one-click wallet integration and free tier make 1RPC accessible to Base’s retail audience, enhancing adoption for everyday apps.

